      "title": "Warrants for Pathum Kerner",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo Additional Magistrate Mr. Harshana Kekulawala ordered today (23rd) to arrest Dr. Pathum Kerner, who was an active member of the struggle, and bring him to court.",
        "These warrants were issued due to the fact that he did not appear in court in relation to the case regarding the incident of riotous behavior during a protest movement held at the Polduwa intersection near Parliament."
      ],
